What Will I Learn?: Learn How To Win  Your Client's Trust

* Freelancing means name hai aitemaad ka (ad wala nahi sachi wala bata raha hn )
* Agar trust develop nahi client ke saath, then you'll be gonna failed.
* Agar client ko trust nahi hai apke saath deal krne mein ya kaam dene mein ya award krne mein toh faid hi koi nahi hai.

4 Important Points To Build Client Side Trust:

* Your Profile: Ap apne baare mein,apne kaam ke baaray mein ,work experience, linked industries, work period ke baaray mein batayein.Kin kin software and tools pr grip hai.
* Portfolio: Yeh woh shelf hai freelancers ka jis mein unke kaam ke baary mein images, links, screenshot (in short proof huta hai kay yeh kaam aata hai employer ko).
* Your Feedback: Agar ap ksi shop se samn lekar mutmain hai toh ap dusre logon ko bhi btayein gaye us shop ke baare mein or us shop ke liye ache alfaaz use krein gaye.Toh yeh bohat zruri hai kay jab ap kaam krein toh apki profiles pr referrals hun, because Seeing is Believing.Book for reviews nahi hai toh koi buy nahi krega ,tou yeh referrals achi baat btarahay hai about your quality of services,communication, deadline meeting, price.
* Profile Videos: Agar apki video apke freelance account mein hai toh client ko foran pata chal jayega apki body langage, confidence, communication ,sense pf knowledge kay apke pas utni knowledge hai kaam ke liye kay nahi sirf videos se client ko pata chal jayega.

*** English is the language that you've to use when you record the Video ***